==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enwallow
<hw>En*wal"low</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To plunge into,
or roll in, flith; to wallow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>So now all three one senseless lump remain,⟦br⟧
<qex>Enwallowed</qex> in his own black bloody gore.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enwheel</ent>⟦br⟧
